Malice/ Organics/ Necross/ Splattercannon/ Hellplague:

Necross and Splattercannon immediatly open fire, while Hellplague moves out of the way.

Malice tries to evade the fire by dashing to the side.  He grabs Organics&#39; sword and drops his disruptor rifle so she may be able to defend herself.  He reduces the light he gives off, but still enough to interfer with vision.  He tries to get up to Blacknightmare but is stopped by a hail of fire.
&quot;I&#39;ll show you how a real Decepticon REALLY fights!&quot;
He shifts the sword to cannon mode.  The blade splits, as does the handle.  The two halves grow in size, until the handle attaches to his shoulders for support.  He aims the massive weapon on Blacknightmare, and begins powering up the cannon charge.

Hellplague decides to get Malice&#39;s attention by capturing Organics.  She succeeds and wraps an arm around her neck and hoists her up.
&quot;Alright Maximals!  Stop this foolishness or your little girlly friend has a weapon accident!&quot; the minion says as she aims one of her disruptors mounted in her arm to the valkyrie&#39;s head.

OOC: Malice is temporarily supercharged.  He has better speed, but endurance and dexterity have suffered.  He&#39;ll take more damage, but he also has all that energy to attack with.  He can use the cannon multiple times, so either evade him, or try and stop him from firing the cannon.  It will be a big bang.  Also, try and get Organics away from Hellplague.  She is weak and needs help.

